snippet.title: Ship Graveyard Simulator 2 | Announcement Trailer | STEAM
snippet.description:
🚢 Ship Graveyard Simulator 2 is coming to Steam! 🔥 
Dust off your hammer - it's time to get back to work! Wishlist now 👇
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2201940

Visit the new beach coast with the largest, biggest ship graveyard in the world, it's time to get back to the business. ⚓ New adventure, new challenges, you have a new job to do. 💪 

—
#ShipGraveyardSimulator2 #shipgraveyard #gameplaytrailer
